cv-cvsu v.0.1.0

CVSU adaptation module for the CV library.

This library contains simple adaptation and conversion functions for using CVSU
library with CV images and types.

Installation:

Haskell platform, CV library, and hs-cvsu library are required for using this
library.

Haskell platform:
http://www.haskell.org/platform/
Version 2012.2.0.0 or newer is recommended.

hs-cvsu:
http://github.org/amnipar/hs-cvsu

CV:
http://github.org/aleator/CV
Note that this requires OpenCV library.
